sequenceDiagram
    participant VAD as VAD Service
    participant ASR as ASR Service
    participant MT as Translation
    participant TTS as TTS Service
    
    Note over VAD, TTS: Time Axis (t) --->
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note right of VAD: Segment 1 (0-3s) processing
        VAD->>ASR: Event [Seg 1]
        ASR->>MT: Event [Text 1]
        MT->>TTS: Event [Trans 1]
        TTS-->>VAD: Output [Audio 1]
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note right of VAD: Segment 2 (3-6s) starts while Seg 1 is still in MT/TTS
        VAD->>ASR: Event [Seg 2]
        ASR->>MT: Event [Text 2]
        MT->>TTS: Event [Trans 2]
    end
    
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note right of VAD: Segment 3 (6-9s) starts pipeline
        VAD->>ASR: Event [Seg 3]
        ASR->>MT: Event [Text 3]
    end